<br>
1. Pets, what are the differences between the Elemental ones, and if u do Monster summoning does that Monster get its special abilities.  IE orc orcle casting spells etc.<br>
<br>
2. What equipment do I focus on? Int only?  I know Enc need Cha (i've never played a pure caster only melee's and my Cleric)<br>
<br>
3. I am gonna be playing this untwinked I like the challenge, I will probley twink after lvl 20 but I like the first challenge at the begining.  Any thoughts on what spells I should focus on since I wont be twinking with money or anything.<br>
<br>
